QGIS algorithm Multiple regression analysis (points/raster)

Source: R/saga_multipleregressionanalysispointsraster.R
saga_multipleregressionanalysispointsraster.Rd

QGIS Algorithm provided by SAGA Multiple regression analysis (points/raster) (saga:multipleregressionanalysispointsraster)

saga_multipleregressionanalysispointsraster(
  GRIDS = qgisprocess::qgis_default_value(),
  SHAPES = qgisprocess::qgis_default_value(),
  ATTRIBUTE = qgisprocess::qgis_default_value(),
  INTERPOL = qgisprocess::qgis_default_value(),
  COORD_X = qgisprocess::qgis_default_value(),
  COORD_Y = qgisprocess::qgis_default_value(),
  METHOD = qgisprocess::qgis_default_value(),
  P_IN = qgisprocess::qgis_default_value(),
  P_OUT = qgisprocess::qgis_default_value(),
  INFO_COEFF = qgisprocess::qgis_default_value(),
  INFO_MODEL = qgisprocess::qgis_default_value(),
  INFO_STEPS = qgisprocess::qgis_default_value(),
  RESIDUALS = qgisprocess::qgis_default_value(),
  REGRESSION = qgisprocess::qgis_default_value(),
  ...,
  .complete_output = TRUE
)

Arguments

GRIDS

multilayer - Grids. .
SHAPES

source - Shapes. Path to a vector layer.
ATTRIBUTE

field - Attribute. The name of an existing field. ; delimited list of existing field names.
INTERPOL

enum of ("[0] Nearest Neighbor", "[1] Bilinear Interpolation", "[2] Inverse Distance Interpolation", "[3] Bicubic Spline Interpolation", "[4] B-Spline Interpolation") - Grid Interpolation. Number of selected option, e.g. '1'. Comma separated list of options, e.g. '1,3'.
COORD_X

boolean - Include X Coordinate. 1 for true/yes. 0 for false/no.
COORD_Y

boolean - Include Y Coordinate. 1 for true/yes. 0 for false/no.
METHOD

enum of ("[0] include all", "[1] forward", "[2] backward", "[3] stepwise") - Method. Number of selected option, e.g. '1'. Comma separated list of options, e.g. '1,3'.
P_IN

number - P in. A numeric value.
P_OUT

number - P out. A numeric value.
INFO_COEFF

vectorDestination - Details: Coefficients. Path for new vector layer.
INFO_MODEL

vectorDestination - Details: Model. Path for new vector layer.
INFO_STEPS

vectorDestination - Details: Steps. Path for new vector layer.
RESIDUALS

vectorDestination - Residuals. Path for new vector layer.
REGRESSION

rasterDestination - Regression. Path for new raster layer.
...

further parameters passed to qgisprocess::qgis_run_algorithm()
.complete_output

logical specifing if complete out of qgisprocess::qgis_run_algorithm() should be used (TRUE) or first output (most likely the main) should read (FALSE). Default value is TRUE.

Details

Outputs description

  • INFO_COEFF - outputVector - Details

  • INFO_MODEL - outputVector - Details

  • INFO_STEPS - outputVector - Details

  • RESIDUALS - outputVector - Residuals

  • REGRESSION - outputRaster - Regression
